{"id": 2378, "genre": 1001, "title": "旅游时哪些细节会让你对一个城市的好感度+1？", "description": "吸引你再去一次的一万个理由。（题图来自：视觉中国）", "record_count": 3524, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180528163734dv59iUqYZkzwsOP7.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-06-28T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 289792, "content": "公交发达，文化底蕴。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1115941}, {"id": 290560, "content": "住在这里的人是幸福的 说什么话都带着笑 然后 有一间安安静静的咖啡厅 一个让人停驻的街角 独特的文化 市井气也令人欣赏。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390239}, {"id": 293888, "content": "交通便利，空气清新，有生活气息。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262462}, {"id": 289793, "content": "清新的空气，温和的天气。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386224}, {"id": 290561, "content": "24小时便利店的数量", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262336}, {"id": 289794, "content": "不根据口音来判断是否当地人，然后使劲坑外地人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377387}, {"id": 290050, "content": "综合感觉吧，比如当地人的热情当地的环境，还有在当地碰见的一些不寻常的事～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378892}, {"id": 289795, "content": "车上行人", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377387}, {"id": 289796, "content": "当地人是否友好，其他都好说", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 787158}, {"id": 290564, "content": "安静，每个人都知道自己的声音分贝", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390404}, {"id": 289797, "content": "司机礼让行人 导视系统规范 公厕方便 移动支付出行普及 便利店繁多", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681738}, {"id": 292357, "content": "市民经常看到带着笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377936}, {"id": 289798, "content": "物美价廉 哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379135}, {"id": 290054, "content": "小姐姐～(￣▽￣～)~", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1323352}, {"id": 291846, "content": "城市干净 人长得好看会穿衣服 建筑不土有特色 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1088059}, {"id": 289543, "content": "很多好吃的！交通方便！街道干净整洁！", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1385203}, {"id": 289799, "content": "幽静，少人……只想安安静静的放空自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174652}, {"id": 291592, "content": "遇见一个“好人” 会让我感到这个城市都变得温暖(｡･ω･｡)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1384606}, {"id": 289545, "content": "建筑有地方特色，街上热闹但不拥挤，有足够多的公园和博物馆", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311182}, {"id": 289801, "content": "细节", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379768}, {"id": 289546, "content": "车辆礼让行人 食物好吃干净", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651076}, {"id": 289802, "content": "初到时，本地人互相自然的打招呼\n白日里，街头巷尾都可以截成风景\n夜幕时，我可以随意任性四处溜达\n离开时，期待和这座城再一次重逢\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386233}, {"id": 289547, "content": "不需要刻意防范被宰", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 740619}, {"id": 289548, "content": "路标清晰 比较容易找得到目的地", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366742}, {"id": 289804, "content": "与城市的人相处的印象很重要，也许城市是座小城市，不够繁华，不够广阔，但人情交往可以使这座城市有着不一样的意蕴。其次是食物，民以食为天，食物是一座城市特有的味道，吃食大抵是地方差最特色了，地域不同，味道也别具一格。熙熙攘攘，人来人往，中国人讲究情义，一个好的印象是刻在脑海里的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386250}, {"id": 289549, "content": "礼貌，友好", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192299}, {"id": 289550, "content": "Grindr上受当地人喜欢的程度", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 414904}, {"id": 289806, "content": "博物馆值得看", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 5538}, {"id": 290062, "content": "比如说司机很礼让行人，比如说街道很干净，比如说在那个城市有个你喜欢的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1387078}, {"id": 289807, "content": "最重要的是基础设施齐全", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1358911}, {"id": 289552, "content": "路标啊，地铁logo啊什么的设计的好看", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1263098}, {"id": 289808, "content": "在哈尔滨问路 连着问了两个路人 都没给我指路 都是直接带着我去目的地附近❤ 超暖", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386262}, {"id": 290320, "content": "十字路口定有红绿灯\n地下通道敢进\n各个景点都有方便的公共交通\n大商场关门晚\n有明确的提示牌，一看就懂的那种", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1382297}, {"id": 289553, "content": "街道整理，厕所干净，遵守交通规则特别是礼让行人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1385644}, {"id": 289809, "content": "美食 文化 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1277248}, {"id": 290321, "content": "态度谦和，行为有礼，用语文明，自觉有序，注意卫生", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1389278}, {"id": 291601, "content": "城市建筑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1393350}, {"id": 296465, "content": "干净", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1419143}, {"id": 289554, "content": "有秩序又有活力，干净又丰富", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 946230}, {"id": 289810, "content": "有好大学，好书店，好博物馆。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 176235}, {"id": 290066, "content": "下暴雨城市排水系统很好，不会被淹", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1387094}, {"id": 289811, "content": "吃的有好多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366539}, {"id": 289812, "content": "公共交通方便！当地人友好！好吃的多！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386273}, {"id": 289557, "content": "出去旅游无非就是吃喝玩乐 吃喝为头 一个城市如果在物质方面不要乱搞 不歧视 不坑外地人 我就感觉这个城市的融合度高 附加值也会提高 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1385641}, {"id": 289813, "content": "和谁一起去", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386274}, {"id": 289558, "content": "问路，当地人很热心指引，感觉这个世界真美好～表白重庆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1385649}, {"id": 289814, "content": "空气。云。阳光。水。绿色。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1384618}, {"id": 289815, "content": "看到很多帅哥美女当然心情好啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1384886}, {"id": 290071, "content": "卫生间干净，心里净化，满足所有强迫这症的恰到好处", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1354604}, {"id": 289560, "content": "非移民城市，环境气候条件好，本地人素质高，有很多好吃的当地特色小吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007288}]}